{"tid":1468470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不割蓆？","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:49:35.000Z","uid":114144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"432fd3927753d95d20d686ffbbe326a7c0e74ac9","tid":1468470,"uid":114144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:42.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫不割蓆？<br />\n和理非同勇武互相配合同尊重理解咪不割蓆囉。<br />\n明明大家理念一致 <br />\n今日小小事都已經好多人想割蓆<br />\n<br />\n成個運動方向發展走歪係好正常 大家都係摸吓摸吓<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">作為和理非應該理解 體諒 與勇武一同承擔責任 如果覺得勇武可以做得再好啲 應該係作出善意提醒 俾建議 而唔係割蓆都割唔切 批評 甚至分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">作為勇武亦應該明白和理非唔係支持暴力 唔係盲撐 勇武所作所為 和理非係會一同受到指責同批評 所以行事要謹慎三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家重新思考乜嘢係不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n回顧返成個運動 都只係過咗半年<br />\n未來仲有好長時間需要抗爭<br />\n大家要團結一致才有希望<br />\n<br />\n認同講俾like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed2d3c3ca9923817c26a86af1b18dd4b82af1a4","tid":1468470,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2